        "subject": "LU-2145 server: move ptlrpc services to the unified server",
        "message": "LU-2145 server: move ptlrpc services to the unified server\n\nCreate service threads as part of unified server. Now threads are\nstarted always upon server start and all targets (i.e. MDT/MGS/OSS)\nset just set of handlers for particular RPCs and register with\nunified server.\n\nThis change allows more than one MDT to work on the same node and\nprovide the next step - unified request handler.\n\nSigned-off-by: Mikhail Pershin <tappro@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Iddad3147cfba15649667dd2229d27d20a3d0ab68\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
